snippet.title: Pox Nora Ronin Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Pox Nora’s 24th expansion, Ronin, is now available!  Along with many new changes and improvements to this collectible, turn-based, tactical, online fantasy game.  This adds 64 unique new runes in total with many new abilities to the battle for control of Poxathuru. 

Visit poxnora.com for more info!
